txt.en: <rgb=#FF0000>You have defeated a Dark-wing warder before Gûrsh has returned</rgb>

Chieftain Gûrsh is a foul uruk with a curious soft-spot in his blackened heart for craban.\n\nTo shatter the confidence of the invaders, defeat Gûrsh and all his Dark-wing Warders together. None of the Dark-wing Warders may be defeated before Gûrsh has returned to the Library.
<rgb=#FF0000>Defeated a Dark-wing warder before defeating Chieftain Gûrsh</rgb>
Chieftain Gûrsh is very fond of his craban-warders.\n\nTo shatter the confidence of the invaders, defeat Gûrsh and all his Dark-wing Warders together.
